
## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python cache files
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Python virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Environment/config files
.env

# Jupyter notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# OS-generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor/project settings
.vscode/
.idea/

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.log